Azure shook off what might have been some sparks that had shot from
Inferno's head, then turned to Hydras.

Azure: I am Predator Councilor Azure, or at least I have been
councilor up to very recently, when I had to... ahem, remove some
compromising information from Maximal hands. What about you? Your
soldier referred to you as "Megatron", but you clearly are not him.
Who are you, Hydras?
